WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.543 --> 00:00:01.691
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.691 --> 00:00:03.160
How have you been doing?

00:00:03.480 --> 00:00:05.720
I just wanted to say hi today.

00:00:06.111 --> 00:00:09.257
I have some things on my heart to talk to you about.

00:00:10.679 --> 00:00:21.436
I've talked to you about angel visitations and things I have experienced with the Lord over the years, but I'm going to talk to you about some more of them.

00:00:21.436 --> 00:00:35.537
Some were angel visitations where I believe we entertained angels unaware.

00:00:35.794 --> 00:00:42.025
My wife has had those experiences, too.

00:00:42.025 --> 00:00:47.400
First off, people wanted to know after the last video, "What do you do with the economy?

00:00:47.400 --> 00:00:51.062
What are you going to do with all that is going to happen?

00:00:52.520 --> 00:00:56.137
" I want to tell you: never be afraid.

00:00:56.137 --> 00:00:59.499
We are always to walk in victory.

00:00:59.499 --> 00:01:02.605
We go from glory to glory to glory.

00:01:03.417 --> 00:01:08.439
We're not afraid of anything—the economy, pestilence, or plagues.

00:01:10.173 --> 00:01:13.207
My recommendation is Psalm 91.

00:01:13.207 --> 00:01:19.689
Get Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 deep inside your heart and meditate on that word.

00:01:19.689 --> 00:01:28.810
The Bible says that when David was talking, he said, "I've never seen the righteous forsaken or his seed begging bread.

00:01:29.200 --> 00:02:02.658
" If He will take care of the sparrows and the animals of the woods—He takes care of it all: fish, flowers, whatever—God is merciful and takes care of His creation.

00:02:02.658 --> 00:02:37.607
We are His sons and daughters; how much more would He take care of you in these last days if you are a true child of the King?

00:02:37.607 --> 00:02:45.756
I'm not worried about any of this.

00:02:45.756 --> 00:02:55.800
People ask if I have anxiety about it—not at all.

00:02:57.240 --> 00:03:10.220
I tell you about it, but inside I say, "This is not for me.

00:03:10.220 --> 00:03:20.053
I'm not participating in an economic crisis.

00:03:20.053 --> 00:03:27.956
" My wife and children will not do without.

00:03:27.956 --> 00:03:37.200
My Father owns the cattle on a thousand hills.

00:03:41.655 --> 00:03:45.400
He has it all in His hand.

00:03:45.870 --> 00:04:09.784
He is the God of the universe, the only God, the one true God, the Great I Am.

00:04:09.784 --> 00:04:30.270
If He dwells on the inside of you, He said He would never leave you nor forsake you.

00:04:30.270 --> 00:04:46.599
Lo, unto the end of the Earth, I will be with you always.

00:04:48.419 --> 00:05:03.080
If that is His promise to you, how much more will He take care of you?

00:05:03.080 --> 00:05:15.196
How much more will He provide food for you and your children?

00:05:15.196 --> 00:05:43.779
Even if the worst came and there was no food at all, He could bring the ravens or mana like He did for the children of Israel every morning.

00:05:43.779 --> 00:05:55.160
He brought them a cloud by day and a fire by night.

00:05:55.160 --> 00:06:06.176
That was under the Old Covenant, the Abrahamic Covenant.

00:06:06.176 --> 00:06:18.951
How much more does He have a covenant with you by His Son's blood?

00:06:18.951 --> 00:06:37.448
Jesus Christ died on the cross for you to be healthy, mentally sound, and wealthy.

00:06:37.448 --> 00:06:46.884
He became poor that you might be rich.

00:06:46.884 --> 00:06:54.230
He became sick that you might be healed.

00:06:54.230 --> 00:07:19.240
2 Timothy 1:7 says God has not given you a spirit of fear, but of power, love, and a sound mind.

00:07:21.586 --> 00:07:41.394
You don't have to have a tormented mind and fear every day because He's given you that mind of Christ.

00:07:41.394 --> 00:07:53.180
Jesus said, "Peace I leave with you, My peace I give to you.

00:07:53.180 --> 00:07:59.385
" He already gave us His peace and comfort.

00:07:59.385 --> 00:08:09.216
So whenever you ask, "Brandon, how are you going to handle all this stuff?

00:08:09.216 --> 00:08:12.169
" stay in peace.

00:08:12.169 --> 00:08:32.140
Goodness and mercy will follow me all the days of my life, and I will dwell in the house of the Lord forever.

00:08:32.140 --> 00:08:44.446
Those are the promises He's given me; that's what I stand by.

00:08:44.446 --> 00:09:08.147
I see all this stuff coming, and when people ask when it's coming, I say this: I'll never go against another man of God.

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:31.079
You might agree to disagree on timing—we all see in part—but I'm never going to talk bad about someone who loves the Lord.

00:09:34.613 --> 00:09:35.973
We just have different revelations.

00:09:35.973 --> 00:09:43.226
Let's be on the same team.

00:09:43.226 --> 00:10:05.828
We want to be winners, victors, and overcomers by the blood of the Lamb and the word of our testimony.

00:10:22.497 --> 00:10:36.488
That's what we set out to do: make the Rapture and stand before the Father and hear Him say, "Well done, thou good and faithful servant.

00:10:36.488 --> 00:10:40.560
Enter into my rest.

00:10:40.560 --> 00:10:47.344
" Who gave the word first?

00:10:47.344 --> 00:10:50.040
Who cares?

00:10:50.040 --> 00:10:59.149
We're all hearing the same Holy Spirit.

00:10:59.149 --> 00:11:04.005
He speaks to each individual.

00:11:06.394 --> 00:11:20.064
The Lord isn't schizophrenic; He isn't talking to Chris or Pastor Steve differently than me.

00:11:31.360 --> 00:11:33.600
But how we interpret and filter it through our flesh is different.

00:11:33.600 --> 00:11:45.215
It doesn't make anyone better or less; it just makes us human.

00:11:45.215 --> 00:11:53.394
We've got to walk in love.

00:11:53.394 --> 00:12:03.560
If I miss it, we walk in grace and love.

00:12:03.560 --> 00:12:14.209
We just keep picking ourselves up and trying harder next time.

00:12:14.209 --> 00:12:18.440
We seek His face daily.

00:12:18.440 --> 00:12:28.783
As my wife says, "I'm just a work in progress.

00:12:28.783 --> 00:12:39.480
" That is a beautiful, humble thing to say because we're never perfect.

00:12:39.480 --> 00:12:49.204
Tomorrow, I'll still be a work in progress.

00:12:49.204 --> 00:12:55.835
Jesus is the only one who's perfect.

00:12:55.835 --> 00:13:11.791
No matter how well you think you hear Him, we're dealing with stinky flesh.

00:13:26.880 --> 00:13:41.060
The only way you're going to get good is by staying under Jesus' wings and saying, "Father, I need You today just as much as I needed You yesterday.

00:13:48.880 --> 00:13:50.493
" That's the only way we go from glory to glory.

00:13:50.493 --> 00:14:06.020
People ask why I'm not upset about the "doom and gloom.

00:14:19.354 --> 00:14:35.204
" I'm here to warn you so we can pray and stop a lot of it, but because we are in the end times, things are going to happen.

00:14:35.204 --> 00:14:44.543
As labor pains upon a woman, so will it be.

00:14:44.543 --> 00:14:55.509
Labor pains don't pause; they increase until the baby is born.

00:14:55.509 --> 00:15:01.320
I anticipate things getting worse in 2025.

00:15:01.320 --> 00:15:24.154
By the end of 2024, we're going to have an escalation, and it will be even more intense in 2025 and 2026.

00:15:24.154 --> 00:15:44.114
If anybody tells you things are going to get better in the world, they aren't reading their Bible.

00:15:44.114 --> 00:16:02.039
I'm not anticipating the world to get better, but I am anticipating a revival.

00:16:10.628 --> 00:16:14.299
I'm anticipating God's children being the head and not the tail.

00:16:14.299 --> 00:16:29.399
Every believer who presses into Jesus can walk in financial victory.

00:16:29.399 --> 00:16:34.028
Don't be discouraged.

00:16:34.028 --> 00:16:46.120
Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:16:46.760 --> 00:17:20.333
I thank You, Lord, that even if there is no food in my cupboards, You are the God of more than enough and You will supply all my needs.

00:17:20.333 --> 00:17:31.091
I am a tither and a giver, and I have tithers' rights.

00:17:31.091 --> 00:17:38.488
He's provided for us time and time again.

00:17:38.488 --> 00:17:53.535
If you have a need, sow a seed in your local church or where you're getting fed spiritually.

00:17:53.535 --> 00:18:00.137
Give, and it shall be given unto you.

00:18:03.987 --> 00:18:15.280
The wealth of the sinner is laid up for the righteous.

00:18:17.880 --> 00:18:26.280
I say, "Devil, I'm taking it out of your economy.

00:18:26.280 --> 00:18:39.844
" When a thief is found, he has to pay back sevenfold.

00:18:40.093 --> 00:18:55.390
You need to get so expensive that the devil thinks twice about messing with you.

00:18:55.390 --> 00:18:59.987
Stand on your covenant promises.

00:18:59.987 --> 00:19:08.679
Proverbs 6:31 says he has to pay back sevenfold.

00:19:09.690 --> 00:19:22.987
We have tithers' rights to walk in abundance and an overflow harvest.

00:19:22.987 --> 00:19:31.815
Read Deuteronomy 28 until it becomes real to you.

00:19:42.394 --> 00:19:42.656
Believe God for big.

00:19:42.656 --> 00:19:48.456
Believe Him for the impossible.

00:19:51.230 --> 00:19:56.548
I believe for supernatural increase, multiplication, and favor.

00:19:56.548 --> 00:20:00.220
Favor follows me around.

00:20:00.220 --> 00:20:05.305
I'm God's favorite kid.

00:20:10.867 --> 00:20:11.787
I even believe for parking places!

00:20:11.787 --> 00:20:15.893
We live by faith.

00:20:15.893 --> 00:20:31.815
Whether it's a parking place or favor for the last can of tomatoes, believe God for miracles.

00:20:31.815 --> 00:20:36.026
Somebody might pay for your coffee—give God praise for it.

00:20:36.026 --> 00:20:40.590
Nothing is a coincidence.

00:20:40.590 --> 00:20:55.944
We believe for things at thrift stores or items to flip on eBay and Poshmark.

00:20:55.944 --> 00:21:01.217
We believe for supernatural sales.

00:21:01.217 --> 00:21:13.111
Whatever you put your hands to will prosper.

00:21:13.111 --> 00:21:20.350
It's time for more in '24.

00:21:20.350 --> 00:21:37.931
I was supposed to talk to you about angels, but I got sidetracked.

00:21:37.931 --> 00:21:46.820
I'll talk about it next time.

00:21:46.820 --> 00:21:57.749
Don't be scared about the economy; that's not for you.

00:21:57.749 --> 00:22:03.480
God is faithful.

00:22:21.533 --> 00:22:33.577
Father, I thank You for every person believing for the impossible, stretching their faith like the woman with the issue of blood who touched the hem of His garment.

00:22:37.559 --> 00:22:45.543
Jesus said, "Daughter, your faith has made you whole.

00:22:48.796 --> 00:23:07.620
" We reach up by faith and grab that hem and say, "Jesus, Son of David, have mercy on us.

00:23:20.520 --> 00:23:21.420
" I agree with you right now for your healing and your miracle.

00:23:29.520 --> 00:23:39.140
We call deliverance over your lives and command those devils to release you.

00:23:39.140 --> 00:23:57.740
We call for healing from the top of your head to the soles of your feet.

00:23:57.740 --> 00:24:11.800
Whether it's a broken toe or a financial blessing, Jesus paid the price.

00:24:11.800 --> 00:24:27.239
We call for marriages to be restored and for peace in your homes.

00:24:28.313 --> 00:24:36.679
We submit to God and resist the devil.

00:24:46.383 --> 00:24:49.965
I pray over your sleep right now.

00:24:49.965 --> 00:25:06.427
If you've been tormented in your dreams, that spirit is broken in Jesus' name.

00:25:11.240 --> 00:25:17.304
Find scriptures on restful sleep and meditate on them.

00:25:35.030 --> 00:25:41.000
I thank You, Lord, that PTSD, thyroid diseases, and glaucoma are healed.

00:25:47.969 --> 00:25:51.433
I stand with Joyce for brand-new kidneys.

00:25:51.433 --> 00:25:55.440
Healing belongs to you.

00:25:55.440 --> 00:26:00.097
Jesus is your healer.

00:26:00.097 --> 00:26:13.226
We thank You, Lord, that we're going from glory to glory.

00:26:13.226 --> 00:26:27.771
If you were saved or healed today, let us know in the comments.

00:26:27.771 --> 00:26:39.069
Please like, subscribe, and thank you for your super thanks.

00:26:39.069 --> 00:26:43.039
Put a smile on your face; Jesus loves you.

00:26:43.039 --> 00:26:50.973
I'll talk about angels next time.

00:26:50.973 --> 00:26:54.835
God bless you.
